FBIS4-19591 "drweu076_j_94001" FBIS-WEU-94-076 Daily Report 19 Apr 1994 ITALY & VATICAN CITY Interim Government Appointments Announced Interim Government Appointments Announced LD1904201194 Rome RAI Televideo Teletext in Italian 1936 GMT 19 Apr 94 LD1904201194 Rome RAI Televideo Teletext Italian BFN [Text] President Oscar Luigi Scalfaro has appointed Prime Minister Ciampi as interim caretaker of the interior, electoral and institutional reform, and overseas trade ministries, while Leopoldo Elia will run the Foreign Ministry and Paolo Baratta will run the Industry Ministry. This was said in a communique from the president's office.
